data.name: Evil Eye Defeat
data.desc: If you control an "Evil Eye" monster: Target 1 monster on the field, or up to 2 instead if "Evil Eye of Selene" is in your Spell & Trap Zone; return them to the hand. You can only activate 1 "Evil Eye Defeat" per turn.

card_sets.set_name: 2020 Tin of Lost Memories Mega Pack
